  "rationale": "<p>Choice D is correct. Expanding the given expression using the distributive property yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 a, squared times, a, plus 2 a, squared times, 3\"></span>. Combining like terms yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 a, squared times, open parenthesis, a, to the first power, close parenthesis, plus, open parenthesis, 2 times 3, close parenthesis, times, open parenthesis, a, squared, close parenthesis\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 a, raised to the 2 plus 1 power, plus 6 a, squared\"></span>, which is equivalent to <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 a, cubed, plus 6 a, squared\"></span>.<p>Choices A and B are incorrect and may result from incorrectly combining like terms. Choice C is incorrect and may result from distributing <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 a, squared \"></span> only to <span class=\"italic\">a</span>, and not to 3, in the given expression.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
